# Normalize line endings to LF for all text files, in the repo AND the working
# tree. This makes behavior deterministic regardless of each machine's
# core.autocrlf setting (Windows defaults to autocrlf=true, which would otherwise
# rewrite these LF files to CRLF on checkout). LF everywhere is the modern default
# and is handled fine by every editor.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary files — never apply line-ending or text conversion.
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif  binary
*.ico  binary
*.pdf  binary
*.bin  binary
*.uf2  binary
*.elf  binary
